title: Twilight (Cambodia 1969 - King Norodom Sihanouk)
description:
Twilight (1969)

Real life Prince Norodom Sihanouk and his wife Neak star in this story of an ailing prince who falls in love with a simple Indian girl. His jealous nurse kills herself when the prince falls for the native woman in this underplayed drama. Insights into Cambodian culture add greatly to the understanding and motives for the characters in the film.

Director: King Norodom Sihanouk
Spoken language: French, Khmer
Subtitles: Hardcoded English (and hard to see at times...)


Rather bad quality, but it is as good as it gets from Russian Market...
